      <Readme>This package installs the Adaptive Rules module for the 
Sitecore rules engine. The purpose of this module is to 
make rules, conditions and actions easier to configure by
providing the ability to make configuration options 
dependent on other options that have already been configured.

This package includes the following components:

* AdaptiveTree macro *
This macro has its root item dynamically selected 
based on the value of another parameter on the condition 
or action.

The following is an example of a condition that is configured 
to use this macro. The first parameter uses the standard Tree 
macro to allow the author to select a vehicle type. The 
second parameter allows the author to select a vehicle 
class based on the vehicle type.

when the vehicle is a [vehicletypeid,Tree,root={4FE677B4-55AD-470A-AB76-68E249DA5472},specific] type that is a [vehicleclassid,AdaptiveTree,dependency=vehicletypeid,specific] class

* AdaptiveOperator macro *
This macro is similar to the AdaptiveTree macro but instead 
of displaying a tree with the children of the item specified 
by the depenedency parameter this macro uses the module 
configuration to determine which macro to use.

* AdaptiveValue macro *
This macro is like the AdaptiveOperator macro but it uses a 
different section of the module configuration to determine 
which macro to use.</Readme>
